Life is short and all things are temporary, so enjoy it while you can and don't worry about what others think
You could be good today but instead you choose tomorrow
Do not disturb yourself by imagining your whole life at once
Be tolerant with others and strict with yourself
The art of living is more like wrestling than dancing.
 It's the truth. I am after and the truth never harmed anyone.
The object of life is not to be on the side of the majority but to escape finding one self in the ranks of the insane.
If it is not right do not do it if it is not true do not say it.
